for_Database

Class Address

  • java.lang.Object
    • for_Database.Address
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Address>

    public class Address
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Address>, java.io.Serializable
    The Address class represents the address information. There are fields for users to enter their first name, middle name, last name, street line, optional street line, city, state and zipcode. The text is gathered to make an address for the contact information.
    Author:
    gtran
